        </div>
     </div>
    <div class='dark-gray' style='font-size:10pt;margin-top:20px;'>
         Here at Oycas we have a vision to combine the power of social networks with the effectiveness of 
         educational management tools to enhance students' academic experience.
    </div>   
    <div class='dark-gray' style='font-size:10pt;margin-top:10px' > 
        with oycas you can:          
        <ul style='padding-left:25px'>
            <li> Register in courses from your own school.   </li>
            <li> Use class oriented discussion boards and live chat to discuss and collaborate.</li>
            <li> Upload and share notes, assignments and exams from each of your classes. </li>
